A true man does not fear
high places, mo!

rows.label: tlk42340111_01_msg0002
rows.name:
To become a legendary salvager,
Kisasa trains all day long,
mo.

rows.label: tlk42340111_01_msg0003

And at night, I eat Grilled Anchortail at
Harapekko Canteen to get plenty
of nutrition, mo!
